lead_paragraph: The U.S. Soccer Federation asked the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission to dismiss a complaint of wage discrimination made by members of the World Cup-winning women's national team.

headline.print_headline: US Soccer Asks EEOC to Dismiss Wage Discrimination Complaint
